	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Gautama Buddha</h1>
	<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
		<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
		<div id="contentSub"><span class="mw-redirectedfrom">&#160;&#160;(Redirected from <a href="/w/index.php?title=Buddha&amp;redirect=no" class="mw-redirect" title="Buddha">Buddha</a>)</span></div>
		<div id="contentSub2"></div>
		
		<div id="jump-to-nav"></div>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#mw-head">Jump to navigation</a>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#searchInput">Jump to search</a>
		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">Founder of Buddhism</div>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">Not to be confused with the Chinese monk <a href="/wiki/Budai" title="Budai">Budai</a> (the "laughing Buddha") or <a href="/wiki/Budha" title="Budha">Budha</a> in Hindu astrology.</div>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">"Buddha" and "Gautama" redirect here. For the Buddhist title, see <a href="/wiki/Buddha_(title)" class="mw-redirect" title="Buddha (title)">Buddha (title)</a>. For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Buddha_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Buddha (disambiguation)">Buddha (disambiguation)</a> and <a href="/wiki/Gautama_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Gautama (disambiguation)">Gautama (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<p class="mw-empty-elt">


</p>
