<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Light_of_Asia_(oratorio)" title="The Light of Asia (oratorio)">The Light of Asia</a></i>, an 1886 oratorio by <a href="/wiki/Dudley_Buck" title="Dudley Buck">Dudley Buck</a></li></ul>
