<li id="cite_note-25"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-25">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFDhammananda" class="citation cs2">Dhammananda, Ven. Dr. K. Sri, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.dhammatalks.net/Books6/Bhante_Dhammananda_Great_Virtues_of_the_Buddha.pdf"><i>Great Virtues of the Buddha</i></a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span>, Dhamma talks</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Great+Virtues+of+the+Buddha&amp;rft.pub=Dhamma+talks&amp;rft.aulast=Dhammananda&amp;rft.aufirst=Ven.+Dr.+K.+Sri&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dhammatalks.net%2FBooks6%2FBhante_Dhammananda_Great_Virtues_of_the_Buddha.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGautama+Buddha" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/></span>
